<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Accès Anticipé | [Ton Produit]</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #6366f1, #a855f7, #ec4899);
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#0f172a] text-slate-200">

    <header class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-white">🚀 PRODUCT<span class="text-indigo-500">LAB</span></div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400">
            <a href="#features" class="hover:text-white transition">Fonctionnalités</a>
            <a href="#pricing" class="hover:text-white transition">Tarifs</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-32 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-8 animate-bounce">
            <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-pink-400 opacity-75"></span>
                <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-pink-500"></span>
            </span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-indigo-300 uppercase tracking-widest">Seulement 47 accès restants</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
            Le futur de votre workflow est <span class="gradient-text">enfin là.</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Rejoignez l'accès anticipé de <strong>[Nom du Produit]</strong> et bénéficiez d'un tarif "Fondateur" garanti à vie. Ne laissez pas passer votre place.
        </p>

        <div id="pricing" class="relative group max-w-md mx-auto">
            <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-pink-500 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-1000"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                    <span class="text-slate-400 font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Offre Early Access</span>
                    <span class="bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 text-[10px] px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold">-60% AUJOURD'HUI</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-baseline mb-6">
                    <span class="text-4xl font-black text-white">49€</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-500 ml-2 line-through text-lg">129€</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm ml-auto font-medium">Accès à vie</span>
                </div>

                <button class="w-full bg-white text-slate-900 font-bold py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-all transform hover:scale-[1.02] shadow-xl">
                    Réserver mon accès immédiat
                </button>
                
                <p class="mt-4 text-[11px] text-slate-500 text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
                    <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-indigo-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                    Paiement sécurisé via Stripe
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border-y border-slate-800 py-6 overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap">
        <div class="flex space-x-12 animate-pulse justify-center text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
            <span>🔥 12 personnes regardent cette offre</span>
            <span>🚀 3 accès vendus ces 20 dernières minutes</span>
            <span>⚠️ Stock limité à 100 copies</span>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
